====Usage notes====
In senses 1, 1.3, and 1.4, the plural is most commonly ''people'', with ''persons'' occasionally used in formal speech or writing. Some native speakers will find ''persons'' inappropriate, even in formal usage. In senses 1.2, 2, 3, and 5 ''persons'' is the only plural.

